[Name] EBTables
[Summary] Linux Ethernet bridge firewalling
[Description]  EBTables is a filtering tool for a Linux-based bridging firewall. It enables transparent filtering of network traffic passing through a Linux bridge. The filtering possibilities are limited to link layer filtering and some basic filtering on higher network layers. Advanced logging, MAC DNAT/SNAT and brouter facilities are also included. 
[License] GPL version 2
[Homepage] https://ebtables.netfilter.org/
